data.description: Suburban Estates features Spanaway Lake Community Access to the lake including a boat launch, dock, and 31 ft of waterfront. Great setting located at the end of a dead-end street.  Large fenced yard with dog kennels and storage shed. Newer kitchen, heat-pump and filter installed 2 years ago, no carpet, and a metal roof. Pierce County Park, Forest, Golf Course, and Sprinker Center nearby. New Refrigerator just installed and the interior is in the process of being painted.
